                                [spacer.gif]
    [spacer.gif] [dophins_camp1.jpg] [spacer.gif] Welcome to the Town of
                                Davie Website
      Davie is where South Florida's finest natural and cultural assets
   culminate into one of the most desirable communities in which to raise
       a family, operate a business, and enjoy recreation activities.

         Located between South Florida's major highways, and near an
    international airport and a seaport, Davie is uniquely positioned to
       provide access to the world while maintaining the intimacy of a
   progressive small town. Davie is the educational hub of the tri-county
    area, presenting opportunities for businesses to hire skilled people,
     and for families to enjoy life-long learning experience. The town's
     diversified economic base and low taxes combine to create a healthy
                                  economy.
